# 🚀 AI Master

> **My Personal AI Engineering Journey**

Designed, Built, and Maintained by **Ravi Verma**

**From Principal DevOps Engineer → AI Engineer**

---

## 📖 About This Project

AI Master is my personal AI Engineering Operating System.

It is much more than a learning website.

It is a complete platform where I will learn, practice, build, document, and master modern AI technologies while transitioning from a Principal DevOps Engineer to an AI Engineer.

This repository documents my complete 4-month AI transformation journey.

Every concept I learn will be implemented through hands-on projects, documented with architecture diagrams, interview notes, and engineering best practices.

The goal is to become job-ready for Senior AI Engineer, AI Platform Engineer, AI Automation Engineer, and GenAI Engineer roles.

---

