# 🛣️ Learning Philosophy

This project follows one simple principle:

> **Build More. Read Less. Learn Continuously.**

Instead of spending weeks studying theory, every concept will immediately be applied to a practical project.

Learning cycle:

```
Learn
    ↓
Practice
    ↓
Build
    ↓
Document
    ↓
Interview Preparation
    ↓
Improve
```

